333
00:18:37,390 --> 00:18:38,760
So I rushed back right away.

334
00:18:39,180 --> 00:18:40,100
Don't blame me.

335
00:18:40,430 --> 00:18:41,890
How could I blame you?

336
00:18:42,430 --> 00:18:44,720
You're the one supporting our family.

337
00:18:46,470 --> 00:18:47,350
