339
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,180
Much better.

340
00:18:52,100 --> 00:18:53,180
Don't worry, Huiru.

341
00:18:53,220 --> 00:18:54,140
Focus on recovering.

342
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:55,070
I'll handle everything.

343
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,260
You'll get better.

344
00:18:58,210 --> 00:18:59,350
