347
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,850
(Should I call Zhu Niannian?)

348
00:19:20,010 --> 00:19:21,930
(It is her mom who's sick, after all.)

349
00:19:23,850 --> 00:19:24,720
(But...)

350
00:19:24,930 --> 00:19:26,890
(she's probably asleep by now.)

351
00:19:31,100 --> 00:19:31,970
Niannian?

352
00:19:36,470 --> 00:19:37,350
Ms. Zhang.

353
00:19:37,890 --> 00:19:39,100
Why are you out here?

354
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,100
Worried about your mom?

355
00:19:43,970 --> 00:19:45,010
Go ahead.

356
00:19:47,430 --> 00:19:48,430
Don't worry.

357
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,760
Just stay calm.

358
00:19:49,930 --> 00:19:50,970
Trust our medical team.

359
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:52,010
Let me tell you,

360
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:53,850
I'm really skilled.

361
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:55,600
Ms. Zhang,

362
00:19:55,850 --> 00:19:57,220
Jing'an told me about you.

363
00:19:57,430 --> 00:19:58,390
