366
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:03,040
Of course.

367
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,430
Jing'an said

368
00:20:05,930 --> 00:20:08,100
her parents save lives as doctors.

369
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:09,470
She's so proud.

370
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:10,760
Really?

371
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:12,760
Actually, since she was little,

372
00:20:13,100 --> 00:20:14,470
Jing'an wanted to be a doctor.

373
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:17,350
