to be a physicist instead.

374
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:18,680
No idea why.

375
00:20:19,140 --> 00:20:21,260
Probably spent too much time
with her brother.

376
00:20:21,350 --> 00:20:22,190
He influenced her.

377
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:24,640
It's a shame.

378
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,510
If we weren't doctors,

379
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:28,930
