400
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:16,140
Why would I?

401
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:18,510
She must have her reasons.

402
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:19,540
Anyway,

403
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:21,510
she's always had her own mind.

404
00:21:22,260 --> 00:21:23,350
But her dad and I

405
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,100
never dared to ask her.

406
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:26,470
We were afraid she'd think

407
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:28,200
we had opinions

408
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,760
about her switching subjects.

409
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:30,940
But we don't.

410
00:21:31,140 --> 00:21:32,070
As long as she's happy,

411
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:33,440
we support her.

412
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:35,970
Ms. Zhang,

413
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:39,100
you're so sweet.

414
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,100
Ms. Zhang,

415
00:21:42,390 --> 00:21:43,850
when do you get off work?

416
00:21:44,890 --> 00:21:46,180
I'm on the night shift tonight.

417
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:49,350
That's so tiring.

418
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:50,510
It's fine.

419
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,510
I'm used to it.

420
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:56,600
Mr. Zhu.

421
00:21:57,760 --> 00:21:58,680
Oh, it's you.

422
00:21:59,350 --> 00:22:01,100
- Yes.
- About my wife's condition…

423
00:22:02,010 --> 00:22:02,850
Don't worry.

424
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,640
The test results
will be out tonight.

425
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:08,470
Just stay relaxed.

426
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:10,140
Trust our medical team.

427
00:22:10,150 --> 00:22:11,040
She'll be okay.

428
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:13,600
Niannian,

429
00:22:14,050 --> 00:22:15,430
your mom's asleep for now.

430
00:22:15,430 --> 00:22:17,470
I'll take you home to rest.

431
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:20,600
You rushed back from work.

432
00:22:20,890 --> 00:22:22,140
Why don't you go rest?

433
00:22:22,140 --> 00:22:23,350
I'll stay with her.

434
00:22:24,350 --> 00:22:25,190
Listen to me.

435
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:26,680
You have class tomorrow.

436
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:30,140
We'll head out first.

437
00:22:30,140 --> 00:22:31,560
Alright, go ahead.

438
00:22:53,430 --> 00:22:54,720
What happened to you?

439
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:56,070
Your dark circles are heavy.

440
00:23:02,850 --> 00:23:03,720
Niannian's mom

441
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:05,220
was hospitalized last night.

442
00:23:05,930 --> 00:23:06,800
What?

443
00:23:07,510 --> 00:23:08,350
Is it serious?

444
00:23:08,350 --> 00:23:09,260
