464
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:46,100
My bad, my bad.

465
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:58,790
I need to tell you something.

466
00:23:58,850 --> 00:23:59,720
What is it?

467
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,050
Promise me first,

468
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:04,390
